%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Army%20Debunks%20Claims%20of%20'Surgical%20Strike'%20By%20Dainik%20Jagran%20on%20Frontpage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23192806%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20An%20infiltration%20attempt%20by%20two%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20through%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Poonch%20district%20and%20the%20subsequent%20killing%20of%20the%20two%20by%20Indian%20Army%20soldiers%20was%20falsely%20attributed%20to%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Csurgical%20strike%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Hindi%20daily%20%3Cem%3EDainik%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EJagran%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20its%20front%20page.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20has%20the%20highest%20readership%20in%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Indian%20Readership%20Survey.%20It%20carried%20this%20misinformation%20on%20its%20front%20pages%2C%20across%20editions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20front%20page%20news%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lead%20story%20in%20the%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2022%2C%20edition%20of%20%3Cem%3EDainik%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EJagran%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20the%20headline%3A%20%E2%80%98New%20Surgical%20Strike%20by%20Indian%20Forces%3A%20Terror%20Camps%20Targeted%20Beyond%20the%20Border.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20by%20journalist%20Gagan%20Kohli%2C%20a%20team%20of%20approximately%2012-15%20highly%20skilled%20Indian%20soldiers%20allegedly%20crossed%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20into%20the%20Pakistani-administered%20Kashmir%20region%20near%20Kotli.%20The%20mission%20purportedly%20aimed%20to%20neutralise%20a%20terrorist%20camp%20responsible%20for%20fomenting%20unrest%20and%20planning%20infiltration%20attempts%20into%20Indian%20territory.%20The%20report%20claims%20that%20seven%20to%20eight%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20operation%2C%20and%20four%20launching%20pads%20were%20destroyed.%20It%20also%20shows%20a%20graphic%20representation%20of%20the%20LoC%20and%20four%20tent-like%20structures%20that%20were%20purportedly%20destroyed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKohli%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20paints%20a%20vivid%20picture%20of%20the%20mission%E2%80%99s%20success%2C%20highlighting%20the%20return%20of%20the%20Indian%20soldiers%2C%20unscathed%2C%20and%20reiterating%20their%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20safeguarding%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20borders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20these%20claims%20were%20met%20with%20swift%20denial%20from%20authorities.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20fact-checking%20body%2C%20the%20PIB%20Fact%20Check%2C%20said%20the%20report%20is%20false%20and%20baseless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJagranNews%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40JagranNews%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPIBFactCheck%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PIBFactCheck%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%9C%94%EF%B8%8F%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B