Mission%20Is%20Not%20India's%20Alone%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Message%20To%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20congratulated%20India%20and%20the%20whole%20world%20after%20lander%20Vikram%20of%20the%20Chanrayaan-3%20mission%20successfully%20landed%20near%20the%20Moon's%20South%20Pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20land%20a%20craft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%5C%22%3Enear%20the%20Moon's%20South%20Pole%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20scientists%20believe%20there%20are%20high%20chances%20of%20finding%20a%20dense%20concentration%20of%20water%2C%20which%20was%20first%20detected%20by%20the%20previous%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20approach%20of%20one%20Earth%2C%20one%20family%2C%20one%20future%20is%20resonating%20across%20the%20globe.%20This%20human-centric%20approach%20has%20been%20welcomed%20universally.%20Our%20Moon%20mission%20is%20also%20based%20on%20the%20human-centric%20approach%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20success%20belongs%20to%20all%20of%20%C2%A0humanity.%20It%20will%20help%20Moon%20missions%20by%20the%20other%20countries%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20on%20a%20video%20feed%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20where%20he%20has%20gone%20on%20an%20official%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM's%20Modi's%20address%20came%20seconds%20after%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20confirmed%20the%20successful%20touchdown%20of%20the%20lander%20Vikram.%20The%20rover%20Pragyan%20will%20roll%20out%20from%20the%20lander%20craft%20after%20over%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20during%20landing%2C%20the%20craft%20had%20kicked%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20fine%20Moon%20dust%2C%20which%20won't%20settle%20down%20due%20to%20the%20Moon's%20weak%20gravity%20but%20will%20drift%20away%20on%20its%20own%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26qu