3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20joined%20in%20the%20event%20online%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20where%20he%20is%20attending%20the%20BRICS%20Summit%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20moment%20is%20precious%20and%20unprecedented.%20This%20moment%20announces%20the%20victory%20of%20new%20India.%20This%20moment%20is%20the%20strength%20of%201.4%20billion%20heartbeats%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20reached%20the%20uncharted%20lunar%20South%20Pole%20because%20of%20our%20scientists'%20hard%20work%20and%20talent...%20Our%20moon%20mission%20is%20also%20based%20on%20the%20human-centric%20approach%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20success%20belongs%20to%20all%20humanity.%20It%20will%20help%20moon%20missions%20by%20the%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20the%20next%2014%20days%20--%20equivalent%20to%20one%20moon%20day%20--%20the%20Pragyan%20Rover%20will%20send%20images%20and%20data%20from%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon.%20After%2014%20days%2C%20its%20activity%20is%20likely%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20given%20that%20it%20is%20powered%20by%20solar%20cells.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20landing%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20number%20of%20subtle%20maneuverings.%20The%20Vikram%2C%20which%20was%20powered%20by%20four%20engines%2C%20will%20cut%20off%20two%20to%20lose%20speed%20over%20the%20last%2030%20km%20and%20achieve%20the%20tricky%20soft%20landing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20successful%20landing%20has%20kicked%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20fine%20dust.%20The%20rover%20Pragyan%20will%20roll%20out%20only%20when%20the%20dust%20has%20moved%20away.%20Unlike%20Earth%2C%20the%20dust%20will%20not%20settle%20in%20moon%2C%20given%20its%20lower%20gravitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20event%20is%20being%20telecast%20live%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ISRO%20website%2C%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20DD%20National%20will%20air%20live%20feed%20from%205.20%20pm.%C2%A0%20Schools%20are%20open%20and%20space%20enthusiasts%20are%20organising%20parties%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20historic%20moment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20moon%20lander%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%2C%20perched%20on%20a%20LVM%203%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle.%20It%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%205.%20The%20lander%20Vikram%20is%20named%20after%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%2C%20who%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20programme.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20moon%20mission%2C%20ISRO%20has%20a%20number%20of%20projects%20lined%20up%20-%20one%20of%20them%20a%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20and%20a%20human%20space%20flight%20programme%2C%20Gaganyaan.%20Aditya-L1%2C%20the%20first%20space-based%20Indian%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%2C%20is%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20launch%2C%20most%20likely%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692795780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F25e4m4co_chandrayaan3-descent-isro-650_650x400_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20moon%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20has%20made%20a%20successful%20soft%20landing%20near%20the%20moon's%20South%20Pole%2C%20bringing%20cheer%20to%20a%20billion%20hearts%20and%20propelling%20India%20to%20the%20elite%20space%20club.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-lands-on-moon-india-joins-elite-space-club-4322798%2Famp%2