%20I'm%20far%20from%20unique%2C%20according%20to%20new%20data%20released%20by%20Antenna%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20measures%20Netflix's%20subscriber%20numbers%20through%20opt-in%20panels%20that%20track%20purchase%20and%20transaction%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntenna%20said%20that%20in%20the%20first%20six%20days%20after%20the%20clampdown%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20Netflix%20had%20%26quot%3Bthe%20four%20single%20largest%20days%20of%20US%20user%20acquisition%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%20Antenna%20had%20tracked%20it.%20And%20new%20data%20the%20firm%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20shows%20momentum%20has%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20chart%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.antenna.live%2Fpost%2Fhas-netflixs-password-crackdown-growth-continued%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAntenna%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20shows%20the%20spike%20in%20sign-ups%20that%20Netflix%20has%20seen%20in%20the%20US%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Graph%20showing%20Netflix%20subscriber%20growth%20in%20the%20US%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e5f98d4c17ff0019bade3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAntenna%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20chart%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20big%20spike%20in%20June%20(and%20late%20May)%20in%20the%20US%20that%20helped%20propel%20Netflix%20to%20a%20monster%20Q2%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-earnings-riding-high-despite-actors-strike-ads-password-sharing-2023-7%5C%22%3Ein%20which%20it%20added%205.9%20million%20subscriptions%20worldwide%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Antenna%20previously%20said%20that%20while%20the%20clampdown%20increased%20cancellations%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-password-sharing-crackdown-success-drives-account-sign-ups-data-2023-6%5C%22%3Eincreased%20new%20