3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20the%20right%20to%20order%20a%20pizza%2C%20or%20give%20their%20email%20for%20a%20receipt%2C%20or%20have%20shopping%20delivered%2C%20without%20then%20being%20asked%20for%20sex%20or%20a%20date%20a%20little%20while%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Emily%20Keaney%2C%20a%20deputy%20commissioner%20at%20the%20ICO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20research%20today%20shows%20a%20disturbingly%20high%20number%20of%20people%2C%20particularly%20young%20people%2C%20are%20falling%20prey%20to%20these%20text%20pests%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20a%20female%20Etihad%20Airways%20passenger%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2023%2Fjun%2F22%2Fetihad-airways-contractor-sent-me-unsolicited-messages-says-british-woman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20she%20felt%20unsafe%20after%20a%20worker%20contracted%20by%20the%20airline%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-worker-sent-unsolicited-messages-to-passenger-using-data-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20her%20phone%20number%20in%20the%20company%20system%20then%20sent%20her%20unsolicited%20text%20messages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20may%20be%2C%20amongst%20some%2C%20an%20outdated%20notion%20that%20to%20use%20someone's%20personal%20details%20given%20to%20you%20in%20a%20business%20context%20to%20ask%20them%20out%20is%20romantic%20or%20charming%2C%26quot%3B%20Keaney%20said.%20%26quot%3BPut%20quite%20simply%2C%20it%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20against%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20number%20of%20firms%2C%20particularly%20in%20delivery%2C%20transport%2C%20or%20logistics%2C%20rely%20on%20gig%20economy%20or%20contract%20workers.%20These%20workers%20are%20not%20entitled%20to%20the%20same%20employment%20rights%20as%20full-time%20workers%2C%20the%20jobs%20can%20be%20precarious%20and%20badly%20paid%2C%20and%20turnover%20is%20often%20high.%20One%20consequence%20is%20that%20sensitive%20customer%20information%2C%20such%20as%20phone%20numbers%20and%20addresses%2C%20is%20accessible%20to%20casual%20workers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICO%20did%20not%20explicitly%20name%20any%20companies%2C%20but%20pointed%20to%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20businesses%26quot%3B%20operating%20in%20food%20and%20parcel%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20survey%20found%20that%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20UK%20public%20believe%20it%20isn't%20morally%20right%20to%20use%20personal%20details%20given%20for%20business%20purposes%20for%20romantic%20or%20sexual%20propositions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator%20said%20it's%20cracking%20down%20on%20such%20occurrences%2C%20asking%20victims%20to%20come%20forward%2C%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20companies%20to%20remind%20them%20of%20their%20data%20protection%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20company%20is%20found%20not%20to%20be%20following%20data-protection%20laws%2C%20it%20can%20be%20fined%20up%20to%20%C2%A317.5%20million%20(%2422.1%20million)%20or%204%25%20of%20its%20global%20turnover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-drivers-asking-customers-sex-dates-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692792473000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e5e7f94c17ff0019bad5e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-drivers-asking-customers-sex-dates-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20the%20right%20to%20order%20a%20pizza%20...%20without%20then%20being%20asked%20for%20sex%20or%20a%20date.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40insider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-drivers-asking-customers-sex-dates-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22REAL%20reas