p%3EThe%20year%20didn%E2%80%99t%20start%20on%20a%20good%20note%20for%20farmers%20as%20unseasonal%20rains%20and%20heatwaves%20destroyed%20several%20crops.%20Heat%20waves%20can%20cause%20wilting%2C%20stunting%20or%20early%20ripening%20of%20crops%2C%20leading%20to%20lower%20production%20and%20high%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnseasonal%20rainfall%20destroyed%20over%2018%20kinds%20of%20standing%20crops%20ranging%20from%20chickpeas%20to%20wheat%20and%20maize%2C%20to%20tomatoes%2C%20cashew%20and%20mangoes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Feconomy%2Funeven-rainfall-impact-pulses-rice-crops-will-there-be-a-price-hike-experts-explain-17349721.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC%20TV-18%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20were%20Rabi%20crops.%20Then%20monsoons%20were%20delayed%20and%20Kharif%20crops%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20eggplant%2C%20beans%20and%20bottle%20gourd%20took%20a%20hit%20as%20well%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20annual%20retail%20inflation%20in%20July%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fat-15-month-high-retail-inflation-in-july-jumped-to-7-44-owing-to-soaring-vegetable-prices%5C%22%3Erose%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20highest%20in%2015%20months%20as%20vegetable%20and%20cereals%20prices%20skyrocketed.%20This%20has%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20government%20to%20take%20action%20to%20bring%20down%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frural-areas-reported-the-highest-retail-inflation-in-december-data%5C%22%3ERural%20Areas%20Reported%20Higher%20Retail%20Inflation%20Than%20Urban%20Areas%20in%20December%3A%20Data%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20inflation%20goes%20up%2C%20the%20purchasing%20power%20goes%20down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20inflation%20goes%20up%2C%20the%20purchasing%20power%2C%20or%20how%20much%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20money%20can%20buy%2C%20goes%20down.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20you%20need%20more%20money%20to%20buy%20the%20same%20set%20of%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20skyrocketing%20tomato%20prices%2C%20even%20McDonald%E2%80%99s%20and%20Burger%20King%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66519700%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20tomato%20from%20its%20Indian%20menu.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20equally%20disappointing%20for%20the%20poor%20people%20whose%20food%20bill%20is%20persistently%20increasing%20amid%20stagnant%20wages.%20A%20person%20could%20afford%20the%20rise%20in%20food%20prices%20only%20if%20their%20income%20rises%20according%20to%20inflation.%20But%20is%20that%20happening%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20inflation%20is%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20Indians%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20due%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArticle-14%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Famidst-a-govt-enforced-data-vacuum-stagnating-wages-rising-costs-increase-economic-distress-in-rural-india-64b4b2b5e641e%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20stagnating%20wages%20and%20rising%20costs%20have%20increased%20rural%20distress%20in%20India.%20In%202016%2C%20before%20the%20Union%20government%20abruptly%20banned%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20notes%2C%20the%20daily%20wage%20at%20the%20Girnare%20%3Ci%3Echowk%3C%2Fi%3E%20for%20female%20agricultural%20workers%20was%20around%20Rs%20250.%20Over%20the%20last%20seven%20years%2C%20this%20increased%20to%20Rs%20350%2C%20Ranjana%20Magar%2C%20a%2055-year-old%20daily%20wage%20labourer%2C%20told%20the%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20easier%20to%20get%20by%20then%2C%20even%20with%20less%20money%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20has%20become%20more%20expensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20A%20daily%20purchase%20of%20250%20gm%20of%20vegetables%20cost%20her%20Rs%2010%20then%2C%20up%20to%20Rs%2020-Rs%2025%20now%3B%20the%20round-trip%20far