%2Fentertainment%2Fbollywood%2Fcreative-people-are-not-afraid-to-tell-stories-they-want-to-we-are-sensitive-not-afraid-karan-johar-8904621%2F%5C%22%3E%20The%20Indian%20Express%20Adda%20in%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dismissed%20the%20notion%20of%20living%20under%20fear%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%20Karan%20Johar%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20%26quot%3Bfilmmakers%20make%20the%20movies%20they%20believe%20in.%26quot%3B%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20Bollywood%20has%20been%20targeted%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%20Following%20the%20untimely%20death%20of%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20the%20industry%20has%20been%20vilified%20by%20a%20certain%20section%20of%20the%20audience.%20The%20%26quot%3BBoycott%20Bollywood%26quot%3B%20noise%20was%20loud%20enough%20to%20disorient%20creative%20minds.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20were%20not%20too%20many%20hits%20in%20the%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20in%20last%20year.%20Amid%20such%20negativity%2C%20have%20the%20creative%20minds%20felt%20frightened%20or%20stifled%3F%20Karan%20Johar%20said%20at%20the%20event%2C%20%26quot%3BCreative%20people%20are%20not%20afraid.%20They%20are%20not%20afraid%20to%20tell%20the%20stories%20they%20want%20to...%20We%20are%20sensitive%2C%20not%20afraid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Johar%20added%20that%20there%20are%20agencies%20to%20help%20directors%20to%20keep%20check%20on%20his%20content.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BConstraints%20have%20always%20existed.%20Filmmakers%20have%20always%20wanted%20to%20make%20films%20that%20are%20sensitive%20to%20issues%20and%20that's%20perhaps%20what%20the%20country%20is%20sensitive%20to.%20Filmmakers%20now%20have%20a%20legal%20department%20who%20will%20tell%20you%20not%20to%20go%20down%20a%20certain%20path.%20So%20there's%20check%20and%20balance%20happening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20during%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyl0kDdh1OkY%5C%22%3ESucharita%20Tyagi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karan%2