0frozen%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20also%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20freezing%20of%20the%20website%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Srinagar-based%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20the%20Kashmir%20website%E2%80%99s%20editor%20Fahad%20Shah%20had%20already%20been%20arrested%20in%20February%202022%2C%20and%20had%20been%20charged%20under%20UAPA%2C%20and%20languishes%20in%20jail.%20A%20former%20trainee%20reporter%20Sajad%20Gul%20is%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClosing%20down%20news%20portals%2C%20YouTube%20channels%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20is%20becoming%20a%20common%20tactic%20by%20governments%2C%20both%20in%20the%20states%20and%20at%20the%20centre.%20Prolonged%20internet%20bans%2C%20as%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20are%20also%20becoming%20common.%20India%20is%20becoming%20infamous%20as%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20deliberate%20disruptions%20of%20the%20internet.%20The%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20calls%20for%20an%20end%20to%20all%20such%20arbitrary%20practices%20that%20bode%20ill%20for%20a%20free%20media%20and%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20press%20release%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20registers%20its%20strong%20protest%20at%20the%20repeated%20moves%20to%20muffle%20media%20voices%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%20the%20Facebook%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20accounts%20of%20Gaon%20Savera%2C%20a%20prominent%20digital%20media%20platform%20that%20voices%20issues%20of%20farmers%2C%20were%20frozen%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20The%20decision%20has%20been%20take