rate%20disruptions%20of%20the%20internet.%20The%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20calls%20for%20an%20end%20to%20all%20such%20arbitrary%20practices%20that%20bode%20ill%20for%20a%20free%20media%20and%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESd%2F-%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Sd%2F-%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20Sd%2F-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujata%20Madhok%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20S.K.Pande%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Jigeesh%20A.M.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresident%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Vice%20President%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0General%C2%A0%20Secretary%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692789007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F06111908%2FPress-freedom.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fclosing-down-news-portals-youtube-channels-becoming-a-common-tactic-delhi-union-of-journalists%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20media%20body%20has%20called%20for%20an%20end%20to%20all%20arbitrary%20practices%20that%20%26quot%3Bbode%20ill%20for%20a%20free%20media%20and%20democracy%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fclosing-down-news-portals-youtube-channels-becoming-a-common-tactic-delhi-union-of-journalists%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Book%20Excerpt%20-%20Eye%20On%20The%20Stars%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Championing%20Of%20The%20Space%20Sector%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESpace%20as%20the%20next%20frontier%20has%20perhaps%20dominated%20the%20discourse%20of%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20early%20emphasis%20on%20space%20received%20tremendous%20boost%2C%20with%20the%20Mars%20Mission%20capturing%20global%20attention%20on%20how%20'frugal'%20innovations%20from%20India%20had%20ensured%20an%20entry%20to%20the%20global%20club%20that%20included%20a%20handful%20of%20nations.%20To%20PM%20Modi%2C%20every%20space%20launch%20was%20a%20reason%20to%20reinforce%20the%20importance%20of%20technology%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%20and%20a%20reason%20to%20remind%20and%20motivate%20his%20young%20listeners%20to%20make%20science%20a%20part%20of%20their%20DNA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sky%20and%20stars%20have%20always%20enthralled%20children.%20Our%20Space%20Program%20provides%20an%20impetus%20to%20the%20children%20to%20think%20big%20and%20reach%20across%20those%20boundaries%2C%20which%20were%20considered%20impossible%20till%20today.%20It%20is%20a%20vision%20to%20inspire%20the%20children%20to%20discover%20new%20stars%2C%20while%20gazing%20at%20them!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20linking%20curiosity%20about%20space%20to%20fire%20the%20imagination%20of%20young%20minds%20was%20visible%20as%20early%20as%20June%202016%20with%20students%20of%20the%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Pune%2C%20designing%20an%20academic%20satellite.%20Giving%20them%20competition%20was%20SATHYABAMASAT%2C%20designed%20by%20the%20students%20of%20Sathyabama%20University%20of%20Chennai.%20Both%20of%20these%20were%20part%20of%20multiple%20satellites%20launched%20simultaneously%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20which%20was%20fast%20developing%20a%20niche%20for%20low-cost%20space%20technologies%20and%20opening%20up%20its%20services%20to%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20February%202017%2C%20the%20ISRO's%20capacity%20for%20multi-satellite%20launches%20had%20crossed%20the%20hundred-satellite%20threshold%2C%20with%20the%20US%2C%20Israel%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20availing%20the%20ISRO's%20commercial%20launch%20services.%20From%20highlighting%20the%20role%20of%20women%20scientists%20in%20the%20development%20of%20Cartosat-2D%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20South%20Asia%20Satellite%20on%20developmental%20priorities%20of%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20consistent%20champion%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20sector%2C%20keeping%20up%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20scientists%20while%20inspiring%20and%20motivating%20aspiring%20space%20innovators.%20The%20students'%20enthusiasm%20over%20space%20technology%20development%20in%20India%20continued%20to%20grow%20with%20recent%20innovations%20like%20Kalamstat%20and%20sounding%20rockets%20as%20well%20as%20the%20use%20of%20NavIC%20by%20fishermen%2C%20(an%20indigenously%20developed%20navigation%20system%20in%20January%202019)%2C%20which%20was%20celebrated%20by%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat.%20Dwelling%20on%20the%20developmental%20impact%20of%20space%20technology%2C%20PM%20Modi%2C%20in%20the%20January%202019%20episode%20of%20the%20programme%2C%20shared%20critical%20statistics%20on%20how%20space%20technology%20was%20contributing%20to%20the%20economic%20development%2C%20apart%20from%20improving%20the%20delivery%20and%20accountability%20of%20government%20services.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Housing%20for%20All%20Mission%20involves%20geotagging%20of%20about%2040%20lakh%20homes%20spread%20over%2023%20states.%20Along%20with%20this%20scheme%2C%20about%203%20crore%205%20lakh%20properties%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MNREGA)%202005%20were%20also%20tagged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20spite%20of%20the%20mixed%20success%20of%20India's%20Moon%20mission%2C%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%20PM%20Modi%20made%20very%20important%20points%20about%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20experimentation%20and%20the%20need%20to%20never%20give%20up%20hope%20despite%20obstacles%20and%20stumbling%20blocks.%20He%20counted%20faith%20and%20fearlessness%20as%20the%20two%20great%20lessons%20from%20the%20mission%2C%20which%20was%20entirely%20the%20product%20of%20Indian%20innovation%20and%20scientific%20endeavour.%20Drawing%20life%20lessons%20from%20the%20mission%20for%20his%20young%20listeners%2C%20PM%20Modi%20spoke%20about%20how%20temporary%20setbacks%20are%20a%20fact%20of%20life%20and%20that%20the%20strength%20to%20overcome%20these%20setbacks%2C%20resides%20inwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20later%2C%20PM%20Modi%20took%20to%20airwaves%20to%20look%20ahead%20from%20Chandrayaan-2%20to%20rally%20the%20nation%20towards%20a%20solar%20mission%20in%20the%20future.%20From%20envisioning%20Gaganyaan%20to%20putting%20a%20human%20in%20space%20and%20motivating%20students%20to%20develop%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20space%20technology%20through%20the%20ISRO's%20Yuvika%20programme%20by%202022%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20tryst%20with%20India's%20space%20programme%20culminated%20in%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20spawning%20space%20start-ups%20in%20India.%20With%20a%20progressive%20policy%20in%20place%20to%20open%20up%20the%20sector%20to%20private%20enterprises%2C%20in%20his%20nine%20years%20as%20the%20PM%20of%20India%2C%20he%20has%20enabled%20the%20tremendous%20expansion%20of%20the%20ISRO's%20commercial%20capabilities%20as%20well%20as%2C%20the%20beginning%20of%20an%20Indian%20space%20industry%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20IN-SPACe%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20space%20start-ups%20like%20Agnikul%2C%20Skyroot%20and%20Dhruva%20Space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20sign%20of%20how%20inclusive%20India's%20efforts%20at%20opening%20up%20the%20space%20sector%20were%2C%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat%20turned%20the%20spotlight%20on%20Tanveer%20Ahmed's%20work%20at%20Digantara%20on%20mapping%20space%20junk%20and%20Neha%20Satak's%20work%20at%20Astrome%20on%20developing%20low-cost%20flat%20antennas.%20With%20750%20school%20students%20working%20on%2075%20experimental%20satellites%2C%20the%20story%20of%20Tanvi%20Patel%20from%20Mehsana%20in%20Gujarat%20epitomized%20the%20spirit%20of%20Mann%20Ki%20Baat%2C%20inspiring%20girls%20to%20dream%20big%20and%20aim%20for%20the%20stars.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20summed%20up%20the%20societal%20and%20national%20impact%20of%20space%20reforms%20most%20eloquently%20in%20June%202022%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFriends%2C%20these%20are%20the%20same%20youth%2C%20in%20whose%20mind%20the%20image%20of%20the%20space%20sector%20was%20like%20a%20secret%20mission%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20but%2C%20the%20country%20undertook%20space%20reforms%2C%20and%20the%20same%20youth%20are%20now%20launching%20their%20own%20satellites.%2F%20When%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%20is%20ready%20to%20touch%20the%20sky%2C%20how%20can%20our%20country%20be%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20The%20author%20and%20publisher%20of%20the%20book%20are%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20book%20or%20any%20excerpt%20derived%20therefrom.%20NDTV%20shall%20not%20be%20responsible%20or%20liable%20for%20any%20claims%20arising%20from%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20book%20including%20any%20claims%20of%20defamation%2C%20infringement%20of%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20or%20any%20other%20right%20of%20any%20third%20party%20or%20of%20law.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692788520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F14tncnao_book-cover_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbook-excerpts%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-eye-on-the-stars-narendra-modis-championing-of-the-space-sector-4321277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20extract%20from%20'Collective%20Spirit%20Concrete%20Action%20Mann%20ki%20Baat%20and%20its%20influence%20on%20India'%20by%20Shashi%20Shekhar%20Vempati.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbook-excerpts%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-eye-on-the-stars-narendra-modis-championing-of-the-space-sector-4321277%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbook-excerpts%2Fchan