ourselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20India%20nor%20Brazil%20are%20likely%20willing%20to%20damage%20relations%20with%20the%20US%2C%20an%20important%20international%20ally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20BRICS%20nations%20has%20condemned%20Russia's%20unprovoked%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20winning%20the%20support%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20south%26quot%3B%20remains%20Putin's%20key%20diplomatic%20aim%20as%20he%20seeks%20to%20break%20Russia's%20international%20isolation%20over%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20war%20has%20spiked%20grain%20and%20energy%20prices%2C%20badly%20impacting%20countries%20in%20the%20region%2C%20and%20increasing%20wariness%20of%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20and%20Russia%20may%20have%20ambitious%20plans%20for%20the%20BRICS%20group%2C%20but%20realizing%20them%20still%20appears%20some%20distance%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20three%20countries%20value%20their%20foreign%20policy%20independence%20and%20retain%20close%20political%20and%20economic%20ties%20with%20the%20West%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20Thompson%20of%20India%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20South%20Africa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-putin-seek-brics-expansion-challenge-us-power-and-dollar-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692788067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e5c6514c17ff0019bac47a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-putin-seek-brics-expansion-challenge-us-power-and-dollar-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BRICS%20nations%20%E2%80%94Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20and%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%94%20are%20the%20main%20geopolitical%20counterweight%20to%20the%20G7.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines