ng%20searches%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPakistani%20bride%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSachinMeena%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SachinMeena%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSeemaHaider%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SeemaHaider%3C%2Fa%3E%20fasting%20today%20for%20the%20success%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3Landing%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3Landing%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20praises%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20said%20she%20will%20break%20her%20fast%20only%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3%3C%2Fa%3E%20lands%20on%20the%20Moon%20successfully.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1Lec5Cn1Zs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1Lec5Cn1Zs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shameela%20(%40shaikhshameela)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshaikhshameela%2Fstatus%2F1694243601948242268%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20she%20is%20seen%20with%20her%20hands%20folded%20in%20reverence%20before%20the%20Hindu%20deities'%20idols.%20She%20says%2C%20''Though%20my%20health%20is%20not%20in%20its%20best%20state%2C%20I%20am%20observing%20a%20fast%20with%20the%20hope%20for%20Chandrayaan-3's%20successful%20landing%20scheduled%20for%20this%20evening.%20This%20accomplishment%20holds%20great%20promise%20for%20India's%20future.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20sustaining%20my%20fast%20until%20its%20successful%20landing.%20I%20offer%20