n%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20So%20you%20were%20the%20goody%20goody%20in%20the%20family%3F%20You%20were%20mummy%E2%80%99s%20pet%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20say%20that.%20You%20ask%20my%20brother%20that.%20He%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20agree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20You%20describe%20your%20family%20as%20an%20old-fashioned%20Parsi%20family.%20At%20another%20point%20in%20your%20autobiography%2C%20you%20call%20it%20a%20traditional%20Parsi%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20true.%20That%20had%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20with%20my%20grandparents%20too.%20Every%20night%20after%20dinner%2C%20my%20grandfather%20had%20my%20brother%20and%20myself%2C%20and%20he%20taught%20us%20our%20prayers%20and%20he%20taught%20us%20arithmetic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20And%20are%20you%20good%20at%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Yeah%2C%20in%20those%20days%20I%20could%20say%20my%2017%20times%20tables%2C%20my%2019%20times%20tables%2C%20and%20he%20was%20that%20typical%20Parsi%20educated%2C%20counting%20on%20his%20fingers%2C%20and%20I%20still%20only%20counted%20Gujarati.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20any%20other%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%20is%20terrific.%20What%20is%2024%20in%20Gujarati%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EZM%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%20came%20from%20my%20grandfather.%20My%20father%20taught%20me%20music%20and%20taught%20me%20to%20appreciate%20music%2C%20because%20he%20sat%20with%20me%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20also%2C%20and%20we%20would%20play%20records.%20He%20had%20a%20wonderful%20collection%2C%20so%20when%20I%20went%20to%20Vienna%2C%20I%20knew%20a%20lot%20of%20music%20that%20I%20had%20heard%20at%20home.%20