20Balasore%20Tragedy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20main%20reasons%20for%20decreased%20punctuality%20are%20%E2%80%98asset%20failure%20and%20more%20construction%20works%E2%80%99%2C%20TOI%20reported.%20An%20assessment%20of%20railways%E2%80%99%20train%20operations%20and%20maintenance%20till%20the%20first%20week%20of%20August%20this%20year%20shows%20that%20there%20were%2014%20%E2%80%98consequential%20accidents%E2%80%99%20compared%20to%20six%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsequential%20rail%20accidents%20are%20those%20which%20cause%20loss%20of%20human%20life%2C%20injury%2C%20loss%20of%20railway%20property%20and%20interruption%20to%20rail%20traffic.%20The%20biggest%20consequential%20accident%20took%20place%20on%20June%202%20at%20Bahanaga%20Bazar%20station%20in%20Balasore%20which%20claimed%20294%20lives%20and%20left%20over%201%2C000%20injured%2C%20the%20TOI%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20performance%20details%20also%20show%20that%20track%20failures%20or%20defects%20increased%20by%2010%25%20and%20signal%20failures%20went%20up%20by%2021%25%20between%20April%20and%20mid-August%2C%202023%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692781210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fslow-and-unsteady-punctuality-of-trains-drops-to-73%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20speed%20of%20freight%20trains%20also%20fell%20to%2027.5%20kmph%2C%20a%20reduction%20from%20the%20previous%20year's%2032.4%20kmph.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fslow-and-unsteady-punctuality-of-trains-drops-to-73%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20planes%20cleared%20to%20t