%20Vishal%20Dadlani.%20The%20film%2C%20India's%20first%20aerial%20action%20saga%2C%20will%20also%20include%20five%20songs%2C%20including%20a%20sad%20song.%20Anil%20Kapoor%20and%20Karan%20Singh%20Grover%20will%20also%20have%20key%20roles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffighter-hrithik-roshan-and-deepika-padukone-to-shoot-for-a-dance-number-choreographed-by-bosco-caesar%2Farticleshow%2F102977734.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Drank%20Water%20From%20the%20Toilet'%3A%20Promised%20Visa%20to%20Italy%2C%2017%20Indian%20Men%20Abused%2C%20Sold%20Off%20in%20Libya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140314%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-21-33.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20Ravinder%20Kumar%20and%20his%20family%2C%20February%206%2C%202023%20was%20an%20extremely%20happy%20day.%20Three%20men%20from%20the%20family%20%E2%80%93%20Ravinder%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20brother%20and%20brother-in-law%20%E2%80%93%20left%20for%20Italy%2C%20looking%20for%20work%20and%20a%20salary%20in%20euros%2C%20which%20in%20Indian%20currency%20would%20have%20easily%20converted%20into%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20the%20Dera%20Bassi-based%20family%20from%20Mohali%20district%20never%20knew%20was%20that%20their%20men%2C%20along%20with%2014%20others%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20would%20remain%20trapped%20in%20Libya%20for%20six%20months%20instead%20of%20ever%20making%20it%20to%20Italy.%20Ravinder%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20paid%20a%20whopping%20sum%20of%20Rs%2049%20lakh%20to%20Madan%20Lal%2C%20a%20Haryana-based%20travel%20agent%20in%20Pehowa%2C%20who%20was%20their%20family%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20realised%20the%20fraud%2C%20the%20family%20got%20an%20FIR%20under%20Sections%20406%2C%20420%20and%20120B%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20Punjab%20Travel%20Professionals%20Regulation%20(PTPR)%20Act%20registered%20against%20Madan%20Lal%20and%20his%20two%20female%20accomplices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ravinder%E2%80%99s%20younger%20brother%20Sandeep%20(30)%20and%20brother-in-law%20Dharamveer%20returned%20home%20on%20August%2020%20after%20facing%20a%20nightmare%20in%20Libya%2C%20his%20son%20Tony%20(21)%20reportedly%20died%20after%20he%20jumped%20from%20the%20window%20of%20a%20fourth-floor%20building%20to%20escape%20a%20raid%20by%20the%20mafia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20aged%20between%2020%20and%2035%20years%20finally%20reached%20Delhi%20on%20August%2020%2C%202023%2C%20following%20the%20efforts%20of%20Aam%20Admi%20Party%20(AAP)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Singh%20Sahney.%20Back%20in%20Libya%2C%20they%20had%20been%20imprisoned%20in%20Zuwara%20and%20Tajoura%20detention%20centres%2C%20besides%20being%20sold%20off%20multiple%20times%20by%20%E2%80%98donkers%E2%80%99%20(human%20traffickers).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Libya%2C%20the%20men%20were%20robbed%20of%20their%20belongings%2C%20including%20passports%2C%20mobile%20phones%2C%20cash%2C%20luggage%20and%20clothes.%20They%20did%20not%20even%20have%20shoes%20to%20wear.%20The%20Indian%20Embassy%20officials%20got%20us%20chappals%20to%20wear%2C%20they%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelpless%20family%2C%20awaiting%20son%E2%80%99s%20body%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Dera%20Bassi%20in%20Mohali%20district%2C%20Ravinder%20broke%20down%20when%20he%20said%20that%20his%20brother%20and%20brother-in-law%20came%20back%20safely%2C%20but%20his%20only%20son%20died%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20flee%20from%20the%20mafia%E2%80%99s%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAsi%20ta%20pehla%20hi%20mare%20si%2C%20hor%20maarte%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20were%20already%20dead%20due%20to%20life%E2%80%99s%20struggles%3B%20this%20tragedy%20has%20ruined%20us%20forever).%20I%20was%20told%20that%20my%20son%20died%20in%20the%20month%20of%20May%2C%20when%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20save%20himself%20from%20the%20mafia%E2%80%99s%20raid%20in%20Libya%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20months%2C%20Ravinder%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20his%20son%20was%20no%20more.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20travel%20agent%20reached%20his%20village%20and%20informed%20the%20panchayat%20that%20he%20learnt%20about%20the%20tragedy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20spoke%20to%20my%20son%20on%20May%206.%20That%20was%20the%20last%20time%20I%20ever%20heard%20from%20him.%20He%20would%20tell%20me%20that%20the%20donkers%20were%20beating%20and%20torturing%20him.%20We%20immediately%20approached%20Madan%20Lal%20to%20bring%20my%20son%20back%20but%20he%20did%20not%20do%20anything.%20I%20am%20helpless%20and%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20my%20son%20met%20such%20a%20fate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETony%E2%80%99s%20body%20is%20still%20in%20Libya%20and%20the%20AAP%20MP%20is%20trying%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20at%20the%20earliest.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sold%20off%20our%20only%20source%20of%20income%20%E2%80%93%20half%20an%20acre%20of%20agricultural%20land%20%E2%80%93%20for%20around%20Rs%2016%20lakh%20and%20raised%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20amount%20on%20loans%20to%20send%20the%20three%20of%20them%20to%20Italy.%20We%20spent%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20per%20person%20and%20sent%20another%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20a%20Pakistani%20donker%20to%20free%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravinder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140420%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-05-28.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140420%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-05-28.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140420%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-05-28-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140420%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-05-28-1024x461.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669353%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Singh%20Sahney%20along%20with%2017%20men%20who%20were%20rescued%20from%20Libya%20at%20IGI%20Airport%2C%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavinder%E2%80%99s%20brother%20Sandeep%20shared%20how%20the%20men%20were%20forced%20to%20drink%20water%20from%20the%20toilet%20and%20faced%20atrocious%20treatment%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20multiple%20donkers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20we%20were%20being%20taken.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20we%20landed%20in%20Libya%20that%20we%20realised%20that%20we%20had%20been%20duped.%20It%20was%20terribly%20hot%20in%20Libya.%20We%20were%20mostly%20given%20non-vegetarian%20food%20to%20eat%20and%20at%20times%20macaroni.%20The%20donkers%20would%20beat%20us%2C%20demanding%205%2C000%20to%2015%2C000%20Libyan%20dinars%20from%20us%2C%20which%20meant%20Rs%2013%20to%2040%20lakh%20in%20Indian%20currency%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20said%20that%20he%20was%20doubtful%20about%20whether%20his%20nephew%20had%20died%20in%20the%20way%20they%20were%20told%2C%20as%20he%20never%20wore%20gold%20earrings%20in%20his%20ears%2C%20a%20tradition%20in%20many%20north%20Indian%20families.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20separated%20from%20my%20nephew%20by%20the%20donkers.%20Though%20we%20remained%20in%20touch%20with%20each%20other%20for%20some%20days%2C%20later%20we%20were%20informed%20about%20this%20tragedy.%20My%20nephew%20never%20wore%20gold%20earrings%20but%2C%20in%20the%20photographs%20%5Bof%20the%20body%5D%2C%20we%20noticed%20the%20gold%20earrings.%20We%20have%20not%20received%20any%20call%20from%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20hope%20that%20he%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20jail%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20praying%20that%20the%20body%20is%20not%20his%20nephew%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonkey%20route%20to%20Italy%20via%20Libya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%2017%20men%20stuck%20in%20Libya%20once%20again%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20endless%20tales%20of%20human%20trafficking%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELibya%20is%20a%20major%20transit%20point%20for%20human%20trafficking%2C%20mostly%20to%20European%20countries.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20days%2C%20we%20were%20prisoners%20being%20treated%20like%20animals%20without%20any%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sandeep%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20perhaps%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20the%20donkey%20route%20to%20Italy%20was%20from%20Amritsar%20to%20Dubai%20and%20then%20Egypt.%20From%20Egypt%20the%20men%20landed%20in%20the%20captivity%20of%20an%20armed%20mafia%20in%20Zuwara%20city%20of%20Libya.%20During%20their%20six-month%20stay%2C%20the%20men%20primarily%20remained%20in%20three%20cities%20%E2%80%93%20Benghazi%2C%20Zuwara%20and%20Tawergha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20till%20last%20year%2C%20the%20fake%20travel%20agents%20or%20the%20donkers%20used%20to%20take%20people%20to%20Italy%20via%20Serbia%20via%20the%20sea%20route%2C%20where%20Indians%20were%20allowed%20visa-free%20entry%20and%20a%20month-long%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20following%20reports%20of%20rampant%20human%20trafficking%2C%20Serbia%20banned%20the%20visa-free%20entry%20of%20Indians%20from%20January%201%2C%202023.%20The%20donkers%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20chalk%20out%20another%20illegal%20route%2C%20were%20now%20opting%20for%20Dubai%20and%20some%20other%20Middle%20Eastern%20countries%20as%20the%20transit%20point%20to%20reach%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClueless%20Haryana%20based%20victims%20narrate%20ordeal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana-based%20victim%20Anmol%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20(21)%20widowed%20mother%20sold%20her%20house%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20some%20gold%20and%20took%20money%20on%20loan%20to%20send%20her%20only%20son%20to%20Italy.%20At%20present%2C%20she%20is%20staying%20with%20her%20two%20married%20daughters%20in%20Pehowa%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol%E2%80%99s%20sister%20Ramandeep%20Kaur%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20her%20brother%20is%20depressed%20and%20is%20suffering%20from%20typhoid.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%20and%20the%20doctors%20have%20advised%20him%20to%20take%20rest.%20He%20has%20turned%20fragile%20and%20is%20not%20in%20a%20condition%20to%20say%20anything.%20We%20are%20indebted%20to%20AAP%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Singh%20Sahney%20for%20bringing%20the%20men%20back.%20For%20us%20it%20was%20like%20a%20rebirth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamandeep%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20said%20that%20she%20met%20local%20MLA%20Sandeep%20Singh%2C%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20and%20home%20minister%20Anil%20Vij%20and%20got%20an%20FIR%20registered%20against%20Madal%20Lal%20at%20Pehowa%20police%20station.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20request%20the%20Haryana%20government%20and%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Sahney%20to%20help%20us%20get%20back%20our%20money%20from%20the%20travel%20agent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20on%20how%20they%20knew%20the%20travel%20agent%2C%20Ramandeep%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20heard%20about%20his%20work%20a%20lot%20and%20he%20lives%20close%20to%20our%20house.%20There%20was%20every%20reason%20to%20believe%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20was%20the%20story%20of%20Ankur%20(22)%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Baram%20village%20in%20Kurukshetra%20district%2C%20Haryana.%20Ankur%E2%80%99s%20paternal%20uncle%20Satvir%20Malik%20was%20the%20one%20who%20helped%20him%20go%20to%20Italy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20that%20this%20would%20help%20bring%20Ankur%E2%80%99s%20family%20out%20of%20poverty.%20Ankur%E2%80%99s%20father%20died%20some%20years%20ago%20and%20his%20mother%20and%20two%20sisters%20were%20dependent%20on%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20said%20that%20the%20travel%20agent%20never%20mentioned%20Libya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20shocked%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20men%20were%20stranded%20in%20Libya.%20He%20had%20informed%20us%20that%20the%20men%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20Dubai%20from%20Amritsar%2C%20where%20they%20would%20stay%20for%20around%20a%20week%20and%20from%20there%2C%20they%20would%20get%20the%20work%20visa%20for%20Italy.%20Nobody%20had%20any%20idea%20that%20we%20were%20badly%20duped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140514%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-21-34.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140514%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-21-34.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140514%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-21-34-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140514%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-21-34-1024x461.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669354%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20rescued%20men%20reunite%20with%20their%20families%20after%20their%20ordeal.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20fraud%20and%20financial%20loss%20could%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20apart%20from%20paying%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20to%20send%20Ankur%20to%20Italy%2C%20his%20uncle%20again%20sent%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20a%20donker%20and%20the%20payment%20was%20made%20via%20Dubai.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20a%20loan%20and%20borrowed%20some%20amount%20from%20a%20local%20%3Cem%3Earthiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(commission%20agent)%20to%20send%20Ankur%20to%20Italy.%20%3Cem%3EHamare%20bache%20ki%20jaan%20bach%20gayi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Our%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20saved)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20thanking%20god%20and%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Sahney.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20story%20of%20Gulpreet%20Singh%20from%20Bhogpur%20town%20in%20Jalandhar%20district%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20twist%20of%20fate.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20cousin%20was%20on%20a%20work%20visa%20in%20Jordon%2C%20also%20near%20Libya.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20he%20along%20with%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Libya%20to%20join%20this%20group%2C%20which%20was%20heading%20to%20Italy.%20And%20he%20got%20trapped%20too.%20Thankfully%2C%20he%20came%20back%20alive.%20Given%20the%20situation%20he%20was%20stuck%20in%2C%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20miracle%20that%20he%20was%20safe%20and%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20cousin%20Ankur%20Kumar%20from%20Patiala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20led%20the%20rescue%20operation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Singh%20Sahney%2C%20who%20led%20the%20rescue%20operation%20and%20facilitated%20the%20repatriation%2C%20said%20that%20he%20received%20a%20panic%20call%20from%20the%20men%20on%20May%2028%20informing%20him%20of%20their%20ordeal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20spoke%20to%20them%20on%20video%20calls%20in%20which%20we%20could%20see%20that%20they%20were%20living%20in%20unimaginably%20bad%20conditions%2C%20without%20proper%20food%20and%20water%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahney%20said%20that%20since%20India%20does%20not%20have%20any%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20Libya%2C%20they%20were%20helpless.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20men%20were%20in%20distress%2C%20we%20immediately%20intervened%20and%20booked%20a%20hotel%20for%20them.%20We%20arranged%20two%20taxis%20for%20them%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20run%20from%20the%20captivity%20of%20the%20mafia%20and%20get%20rescued.%20On%20June%2013%2C%20we%20initiated%20the%20rescue%20operation%20and%20successfully%20rescued%20the%20young%20men.%20That%20night%2C%20I%20and%20my%20staff%20remained%20constantly%20in%20touch%20with%20them%20till%20they%20reached%20the%20hotel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20further%20shared%20that%20even%20the%20rescue%20operation%20was%20a%20roller%20coaster%20ride.%20Two%20days%20after%20the%20men%20reached%20the%20hotel%2C%20its%20owner%20duped%20them%20and%20informed%20the%20Libyan%20Police%20of%20their%20stay.%20The%20men%20were%20sent%20to%20a%20jail%20in%20Tripoli%2C%20Libya%E2%80%99s%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20MP%20requested%20the%20nearest%20Indian%20Embassy%20which%20was%20in%20Tunisia%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter.%20The%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Tunisia%20contacted%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20release%20the%20men%20from%20the%20Libyan%20jail%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%20and%20repatriate%20them%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20weeks%20of%20correspondence%20and%20persistent%20requests%20at%20many%20levels%20from%20our%20side%2C%20on%20July%2030%2C%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%2C%20Tunisia%20was%20able%20to%20get%20counsellor%20access%20through%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20the%20men%20were%20released%20from%20the%20jail.%20They%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20Port%20of%20Illegal%20Immigrants%20in%20Tripoli%2C%20Libya.%20Then%20finally%20on%20August%2019%2C%20all%20the%20paperwork%20and%20other%20formalities%20were%20completed%20and%20the%20men%20boarded%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sahney%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20said%20that%20he%20was%20focusing%20on%20the%20legal%20action%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20unscrupulous%20agents%20who%20duped%20these%20men%2C%20and%20on%20bringing%20back%20four%20others%20who%20were%20still%20stuck%20in%20Libya.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20of%20Punjab%20Police%20against%20Human%20Trafficking%20and%20officials%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20guilty%20are%20booked%20and%20strict%20action%20is%20taken%20against%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692779820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23140314%2FPHOTO-2023-08-22-11-21-33.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdrank-water-from-the-toilet-promised-visa-to-italy-17-indian-men-abused-sold-off-in-libya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Vikramjit%20Singh%20Sahney%20and%20his%20team%20have%20been%20credited%20with%20the%20men's%20safe%20return%20back%20to%20India.%20One%20young%20man%20reportedly%20died%20by%20suicide%20to%20escape%20the%20mafia%20in%20Libya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdrank-water-from-the-toilet-promised-visa-to-italy-17-indian-men-abused-sold-off-in-libya%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20gives%20everyone%20the%20freedom%20to%20play%20their%20natural%20game%3A%20Gill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692779642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102977171%2Cimgsize-59800.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Frohit-sharma-gives-everyone-the-freedom-to-play-their-natural-game-shubman-gill%2Farticleshow%2F102977189.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Talking%20about%20batting%20with%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20young%20Indian%20batter%20Shubman%20Gill%20said%20the%20skipper%20gives%20eve