-at-lack-of-signings-12945627%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmalaga-fans-pretend-random-visitor-is-spanish-football-clubs-new-player-in-prank-protest-at-lack-of-signings-12945627%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmalaga-fans-pretend-random-visitor-is-spanish-football-clubs-new-player-in-prank-protest-at-lack-of-signings-12945627%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Mulls%20New%20Role%20of%20'Chief%20Investigation%20Officer%20of%20India'%20for%20Outgoing%20ED%20Chief%20Mishra%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F15174623%2FSKMishra_EDdirector_141120_1200.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20mulling%20the%20idea%20of%20creating%20a%20new%20post%20of%20chief%20investigation%20officer%20of%20India%20(CIO)%20to%20whom%20will%20report%20the%20chiefs%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2F2023%2Faug%2F23%2Fchief-investigation-officer-of-india-new-oversight-body-may-be-coming-for-ed-and-cbi-2607917.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20likely%2C%20the%20current%20chief%20of%20ED%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20could%20be%20made%20the%20first%20CIO%20before%20he%20demits%20his%20existing%20office%20on%20September%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CIO%20would%20directly%20report%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%20much%20like%20the%20chief%20of%20defence%20staff%20(CDS)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20post%20which%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20created%20in%202019.%20The%20chiefs%20of%20three%20defence%20services%20report%20to%20the%20CDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20sources%20in%20the%20government%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20new%20role%20of%20CIO%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20bring%20better%20synergy%20between%20them%20%5BCBI%20and%20ED%5D%E2%80%9D.%20While%20the%20ED%20primarily%20deals%20with%20financial%20fraud%2C%20including%20cases%20related%20to%20money%20laundering%20and%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA)%20violations%2C%20the%20CBI%20probes%20corruption%20cases.%20The%20%E2%80%9Coverlap%E2%80%9D%20during%20investigations%20necessitates%20the%20creation%20of%20such%20a%20new%20institution%2C%20officials%20in%20the%20know%20of%20things%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%20who%20could%20possibly%20take%20over%20as%20the%20first%20CIO%20was%20recently%20allowed%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20post%20of%20ED%20chief%20until%20September%2015%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20public%20and%20national%20interest%E2%80%9D%20while%20turning%20down%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20plea%20to%20give%20him%20a%20third%20extension%20of%20one%20year.%20Mishra%20has%20presided%20over%20the%20ED%20since%202018.%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20at%20the%20ED%20has%20seen%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-target-opposition-dissenters%5C%22%3Esurge%20in%20stringent%20enforcement%20against%20opposition%20politicians%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20earning%20both%20commendations%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20pulled%20up%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20its%20repeated%20extensions%20to%20Mishra.%20It%20wondered%20if%20any%20%E2%80%9Cone%20person%20can%20be%20so%20indispensable%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20there%20no%20other%20person%20in%20the%20organisation%20who%20can%20do%20his%20job%3F%20Can%20one%20person%20be%20so%20indispensable%3F%E2%80%9D%20a%20Bench%20headed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D