2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeiTy)%20informed%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20that%20it%20will%20incorporate%20rules%20to%20regulate%20the%20use%20of%20vulgar%20language%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwill-incorporate-rules-regulate-bad-words-vulgar-language-social-media-platforms-central-government-delhi-high-court%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeitY%20made%20the%20submission%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20an%20earlier%20ruling%20of%20the%20court%2C%20through%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccompliance%20report%E2%80%9D%20submitted%20before%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20took%20note%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20observations%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20the%20web-series%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECollege%20Romance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20ministry%20added%20that%20regulating%20social%20media%20is%20a%20policy%20decision%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20appropriate%20regulations%20will%20be%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20a%20policy%20decision%20and%20having%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20concerns%20of%20this%20Court%20expressed%20through%20its%20directions%2C%20the%20concerned%20Ministry%2C%20while%20undertaking%20its%20regular%20exercise%20of%20policy%20making%2C%20will%20incorporate%20rules%2Fregulations%20to%20regulate%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20intermediaries%20for%20making%20it%20safer%20from%20the%20use%20of%20vulgar%20language%20including%20profanity%2C%20bad%20words%2C%20etc.%2C%20as%20per%20the%20judgment%20of%20this%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Justice%20Sharma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwill-incorporate-rules-regulate-bad-words-vulgar-language-social-media-platforms-central-government-delhi-high-court%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20August%2017%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20examined%20the%20status%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20observed%20that%20because%20it%20is%20a%20policy%20decision%2C%20it%20is%20sufficient%20compliance%20of%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Court.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Court%20has%20been%20assured%20that%20the%20concerns%20of%20this%20Court%20expressed%20through%20the%20said%20judgment%20will%20be%20incorporated%20in%20the%20future%20rules%20and%20regulations%20which%20will%20be%20shortly%20undertaken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20the%20court%20had%20severely%20criticised%20the%20web%20series%20and%20its%20use%20of%20profane%20language.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwill-incorporate-rules-regulate-bad-words-vulgar-language-social-media-platforms-central-government-delhi-high-court%5C%22%3Erefusing%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20actors%20and%20makers%20of%20the%20show%2C%20the%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20take%20steps%20for%20enforcing%20stricter%20application%20of%20its%20IT%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FIR%20alleged%20that%20Episode%205%20of%20Season%201%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECollege%20Romance%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eshowcased%20indecent%20representation%20or%20obscene%20portrayal%20of%20girls%20or%20women%20in%20the%20worst%20form%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%