22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20highly%20anticipated%20action%20thriller%20'King%20of%20Kotha'%20is%20generating%20immense%20buzz%20as%20it%20nears%20its%20release%20on%20August%2024.%20The%20film%20has%20already%20achieved%20impressive%20pre-sales%20of%20around%20Rs%202.75%20crore%2C%20with%20over%201%2C81%2C862%20tickets%20sold%20across%201574%20shows.%20Social%20media%20is%20abuzz%20with%20discussions%20and%20trending%20hashtags%20about%20the%20film's%20potential.%20Starring%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%20and%20Aishwarya%20Lekshmi%2C%20the%20movie%20promises%20to%20be%20an%20adrenaline-pumping%20experience%2C%20with%20fans%20eagerly%20awaiting%20its%20release.%20The%20cast%20and%20crew%20have%20expressed%20their%20gratitude%20for%20the%20overwhelming%20support%20and%20love%20the%20film%20has%20received.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmalayalam%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fking-of-kotha-surpasses-rs-2-75-crore-in-pre-sales-across-kerala%2Farticleshow%2F102973287.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Remembering%20Howard%20Spodek%2C%20a%20Historian%20Who%20Saw%20Gujarat%20and%20Ahmedabad%20Like%20No%20Other%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23121525%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHoward%20Spodek%2C%20former%20professor%20of%20history%20at%20Temple%20University%20and%20America%E2%80%99s%20leading%20expert%20on%20Gujarat%2C%20passed%20away%20August%2020%2C%202023.%20He%20had%20suffered%20a%20stroke%20while%20in%20Ahmedabad%20in%20January.%20He%20returned%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%20February%20where%20he%20had%20been%20at%20a%20care%20facility%20for%20some%20time.%20He%20was%2081%20years%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpodek%20had%20a%20history%20of%20association%20with%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmedabad%20that%20dates%20back%20almost%2060%20years.%20He%20first%20came%20to%20the%20city%20as%20a%20Fulbright%20Fellow%20when%20he%20was%20a%20graduate%20student%20in%201964%2C%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20teach%20English%20at%20H.K.%20Arts%20College%20for%20a%20year.%20He%20soon%20requested%20an%20extension%20and%20stayed%20a%20second%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpon%20returning%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20he%20completed%20his%20PhD%20thesis%20on%20Indian%20history.%20A%20revised%20version%20of%20the%20thesis%2C%20on%20rural-urban%20integration%20in%20Saurashtra%2C%20was%20published%20in%201976.%20The%20thesis%20examined%20the%20historical%20relationships%20and%20conflicts%20between%20merchants%2C%20literate%20professionals%20and%20political%20rulers%20in%20Saurashtra%20from%20the%20colonial%20era%20into%20the%20post-independence%20period.%20He%20also%20wrote%20perhaps%20his%20most%20famous%20article%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F2942919%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20Origins%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Ideology%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20during%20this%20time.%20It%20examined%20the%20way%20the%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20techniques%20of%20protest%20in%20national%20movements%20had%20been%20influenced%20by%20traditions%20forms%20of%20political%20expression%20derived%20from%20Saurashtra%2C%20where%20he%20had%20grown%20up.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpodek%20became%20a%20professor%20at%20Temple%20University%20in%20Philadelphia%20in%201972%20and%20had%20a%20lengthy%20career%20teaching%20there%20with%20specialties%20in%20Indian%20history%20and%20urban%20studies.%20Much%20of%20his%20scholarship%20focused%20on%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20included%20important%20pieces%20on%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20and%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20industrialisation.%20And%20he%20continued%20to%20return%20to%20India%20to%20do%20research%20and%20maintain%20his%20ties%20with%20friends%20and%20social%20leaders%20in%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%20He%20had%20strong%20contacts%20with%20such%20organisations%20as%20the%20Center%20for%20Environmental%20Planning%20and%20Technology%2C%20SEWA%20(the%20Self-Employed%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Organisation)%20and%20many%20more.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20recently%2C%20he%20became%20connected%20to%20the%20newly%20established%20Ahmedabad%20University%20and%20was%20the%20Shrenik%20Lalbhai%20Professor%20there.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20much%20of%20his%20career%2C%20Spodek%20was%20also%20involved%20(along%20with%20Devavrat%20Pathak%20and%20John%20Wood)%20in%20translating%20the%20six-volume%20autobiography%20of%20Indulal%20Yagnik%2C%20a%20major%20politician%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Mahagujarat%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20384px)%2085vw%2C%20384px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23114335%2F61qZgJmz5pL._SX382_BO1204203200_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23114335%2F61qZgJmz5pL._SX382_BO1204203200_.jpg%20384w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23114335%2F61qZgJmz5pL._SX382_BO1204203200_-231x300.jpg%20231w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669308%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22499%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20World%E2%80%99s%20History%2C%20Howard%20Spodek%2C%20Pearson%2C%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpodek%20also%20was%20well%20known%20in%20the%20US%20for%20his%20work%20promoting%20the%20teaching%20of%20world%20history%20and%20for%20devising%20texts%20for%20use%20by%20American%20high%20school%20students%20in%20the%20classroom.%20His%20textbook%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20World%E2%80%99s%20History%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(2006)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Enow%20gone%20through%20five%20editions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20awarded%20a%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20for%20his%20contributions%20in%20this%20field%20from%20the%20World%20History%20Association%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpodek%20was%20a%20major%20advocate%20of%20Indian%20studies%20in%20the%20US.%20At%20Temple%20he%20provided%20guidance%20for%20many%20a%20post-graduate%20student%20working%20on%20India%2C%20including%20the%20author%20of%20this%20article%20and%20such%20scholars%20as%20Sumathi%20Ramaswamy%2C%20who%20is%20now%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Institute%20of%20Indian%20Studies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20He%20furnished%20similar%20support%20for%20many%20young%20scholars%20in%20India.%20He%20was%20more%20than%20a%20valuable%20advisor%2C%20he%20was%20a%20great%20listener%20who%20engaged%20everyone%20with%20his%20thoughtful%20questions%20about%20their%20interests.%20Several%20officers%20of%20the%20American%20Institute%20of%20Indian%20Studies%20have%20written%20me%20in%20the%20past%20two%20days%20in%20praise%20of%20his%20service%20to%20the%20AIIS%2C%20a%20major%20organisation%20devoted%20to%20promoting%20the%20study%20of%20India%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20much%20of%20his%20career%2C%20Spodek%20was%20intensely%20involved%20in%20studying%20Indian%20urban%20history%20and%20particularly%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20became%20especially%20interested%20in%20understanding%20the%20causes%20of%20violence%20in%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20post-independence%20history%2C%20writing%20two%20important%20articles%20on%20the%20subject%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EModern%20Asian%20Studies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20article%20on%20the%20riots%20in%20Ahmedabad%20in%201985%20differed%20from%20other%20articles%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20which%20had%20discussed%20the%20motivations%20of%20the%20participants%20in%20crowd%20violence%2C%20such%20as%20anti-reservation%20sentiment.%20Instead%20he%20looked%20at%20changes%20in%20the%20larger%20political%20context%20that%20had%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20exert%20control%20over%20the%20violence%20once%20it%20started.%20He%20particularly%20focused%20on%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20authority%20of%20local%20political%20institutions%20like%20the%20Gandhian%20Congress%2C%20the%20Textile%20Labour%20Association%20and%20the%20traditional%20merchant-industrial%20community.%20He%20also%20wrote%20extensively%20on%20the%202002%20communal%20violence%20in%20the%20city.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20he%20developed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffilmfreeway.com%2F2241%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20short%20and%20powerful%20film%20with%20Warren%20Bass%20on%20the%20displacement%20of%20local%20hawkers%20and%20residents%20from%20the%20riverfront%20area%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20film%20was%20based%20on%20interviews%20both%20with%20the%20planners%20of%20the%20riverfront%20park%20and%20people%20who%20had%20been%20displaced%20by%20it%20but%20who%20had%20not%20been%20compensated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbbc-documentary-gujarat-2002-india-truth%5C%22%3EBBC%20Documentary%20on%20Gujarat%202002%20Reminds%20Us%20That%20We%20Are%20Not%20Interested%20in%20the%20Truth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20260px)%2085vw%2C%20260px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23115804%2F71-zuj6TtGL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22260%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23115804%2F71-zuj6TtGL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20667w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23115804%2F71-zuj6TtGL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-200x300.jpg%20200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669321%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAhmedabad%3A%20Shock%20City%20of%20Twentieth-Century%20India%2C%20Howard%20Spodek%2C%20Indiana%20University%20Press%2C%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20crowning%20achievement%20of%20Spodek%E2%80%99s%20career%20perhaps%20was%20his%202011%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAhmedabad%3A%20Shock%20City%20of%20Twentieth-Century%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20much%20of%20the%20most%20serious%20writing%20on%20Ahmedabad%20by%20historians%20had%20focused%20on%20economic%20and%20social%20changes%20in%20the%20city%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20Spodek%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20in%20elucidating%20important%20political%20developments%2C%20including%20political%20violence%2C%20and%20the%20role%20of%20key%20political%20leaders%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%2020th-century%20past.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20of%20Spodek%E2%80%99s%20strong%20familiarity%20with%20source%20materials%20on%20Ahmedabad%20and%20his%20extensive%20discussions%20with%20scholars%20and%20other%20residents%2C%20the%20book%20was%20able%20to%20chart%20transitions%20in%20the%20character%20of%20the%20city%20during%20the%2020th%20century%20in%20a%20way%20that%20few%20studies%20of%20cities%20in%20India%20had%20done.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%20with%20most%20books%20published%20by%20western%20scholars%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAhmedabad%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20written%20with%20a%20local%20audience%20in%20mind%20as%20well%20as%20an%20academic%20one%2C%20and%20clearly%20reflected%20a%20love%20of%20the%20city.%20It%20has%20been%20widely%20read%20and%20discussed%20in%20Ahmedabad%20since%20the%20time%20it%20was%20published.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpodek%20continued%20his%20interaction%20with%20the%20city%20after%20he%20completed%20this%20important%20study%2C%20and%20he%20was%20planning%20to%20carry%20out%20further%20valuable%20and%20interesting%20projects.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnfortunately%20he%20will%20not%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20complete%20this%20work%20now.%20But%20he%20has%20left%20for%20us%20an%20impressive%20and%20inspiring%20legacy%20of%20scholarship%20as%20well%20as%20a%20host%20of%20friendships%20and%20memories%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDouglas%20Haynes%20is%20professor%20of%20history%20at%20Dartmouth%20College.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffaculty-directory.dartmouth.edu%2Fdouglas-e-haynes%5C%22%3Especialises%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20history%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%20and%20teaches%20courses%20on%20modern%20South%20Asia%2C%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692774006000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23121525%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhoward-spodek-obituary-gujarat-ahmedabad-india-studies-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Spodek%E2%80%99s%20strong%20familiarity%20with%20source%20materials%20on%20Ahmedabad%20and%20extensive%20research%20meant%20that%20his%20work%20was%20able%20to%20chart%20transitions%20in%20the%20character%20of%20the%20city%20during%20the%2020th%20century%20in%20a%20way%20that%20few%20studies%20of%20cities%20in%20India%20had%20done.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhoward-spodek-obituary-gujarat-ahmedabad-india-studies-history%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lena%20Endre%20to%20Reprise%20%E2%80%98Faithless%E2%80%99%20Role%20in%20