-boc-signs-financing-pact-for-10-airbus-aircraft-with-indigo-123082300259_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20'Kantara%202'%20boast%20of%20a%20125%20cr%20budget%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692772454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102971692%2Cimgsize-73046.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkantara-2-has-rishab-shetty-increased-the-budget-for-the-prequel-by-over-rs-100-crore-heres-what-we-know-%2Farticleshow%2F102971692.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102971692.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20makers%20of%20the%20successful%20movie%20'Kantara'%20are%20now%20working%20on%20a%20prequel%2C%20'Kantara%202'%2C%20which%20is%20reportedly%20being%20made%20on%20a%20budget%20of%20Rs%20125%20crore.%20The%20prequel%20will%20be%20set%20in%20Mangalore%2C%20unlike%20the%20first%20part%20which%20was%20set%20in%20Kundapura.%20The%20team%20aims%20to%20start%20shooting%20from%20November%202023%20and%20release%20the%20film%20in%20late%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkantara-2-has-rishab-shetty-increased-the-budget-for-the-prequel-by-over-rs-100-crore-heres-what-we-know-%2Farticleshow%2F102971692.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Bill%20Meant%20to%20Replace%20IPC%20Removes%20Safeguards%20Against%20False%20Implication%20in%20Terror%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F06133827%2FUntitled-design-2021-03-06T133816.115.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EUnder%20the%20newly%20proposed%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20Bill%2C%20there%20are%20no%20procedural%20safeguards%20against%20false%20implication%20in%20terrorism-related%20cases%2C%20including%20even%20those%20present%20under%20anti-terror%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA)%2C%20lawyer%20M.S.%20Khan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcausing-floods-is-a-terrorist-offence-in-proposed-law-to-replace-indian-penal-code%2Farticle67223509.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20safeguards%20have%20been%20bypassed%20in%20the%20new%20law.%20Now%20any%20police%20officer%20can%20register%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20anyone%20saying%20the%20person%20is%20a%20terrorist.%20These%20kinds%20of%20offences%20are%20not%20general%20offences%2C%20otherwise%2C%20they%20would%20have%20been%20incorporated%20in%20the%20general%20law%20earlier%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Khan%2C%20who%20specialises%20in%20terror-related%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20British-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20%E2%80%93%20defines%20terrorism%20as%20a%20separate%20offence%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20part%20of%20a%20general%20law.%20The%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%20is%20a%20special%20law%20focused%20on%20terrorist%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20MCOCA%20and%20the%20UAPA%2C%20Khan%20says%20there%20are%20provisions%20that%20before%20an%20FIR%20is%20filed%2C%20there%20should%20be%20approval%20from%20a%20senior%20police%20officer.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20investigation%20into%20such%20cases%20can%20only%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20a%20particular%20rank.%20Third%2C%20there%20is%20a%20bar%20on%20the%20court%20in%20taking%20cognisance%20of%20such%20cases%20without%20government%20sanctions%2C%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20safeguards%2C%20he%20says%2C%20are%20missing%20in%20the%20proposed%20law.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20safeguards%20are%20not%20there%2C%20the%20trial%20cannot%20proceed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20new%20Bill%20considers%20causing%20%E2%80%9Cfloods%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20terrorist%20act.%20Defining%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%E2%80%9D%2C%20Section%20111%20(6)%20(a)%20of%20the%20Bill%20says%20any%20person%20who%20%E2%80%9Cdevelops%2C%20manufactures%2C%20possesses%2C%20acquires%2C%20transports%2C%20supplies%20or%20uses%20weapons%2C%20explosives%2C%20or%20releases%20nuclear%2C%20radiological%20or%20other%20dangerous%20substance%2C%20or%20cause%20fire%2C%20floods%20or%20explosions%E2%80%9D.%20For%20offences%20defined%20under%20Section%20111%2C%20the%20minimum%20punishment%20is%20five-year%20jail%20and%20the%20maximum%20punishment%20is%20a%20death%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20might%20appear%20strange%20that%20a%20disaster%20such%20as%20floods%20can%20be%20blamed%20on%20some%20individual%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20enact%20a%20law%20to%20counter%20that%2C%20it%20may%20be%20recalled%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Assam%20has%20already%20set%20a%20precedent%20in%20prosecuting%20those%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fflood-jihad-media-outlets-communalise-silchar-floods%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cman-made%E2%80%9D%20floods%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20year%20in%20August%2C%20the%20Assam%20Police%20arrested%20four%20Muslims%20after%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20had%20accused%20them%20creating%20of%20%E2%80%9Cman-made%E2%80%9D%20floods.%20Sarma%20had%20added%20that%20the%20embankment%20along%20the%20Barak%20River%20was%20breached%20by%20some%20people.%20Several%20social%20media%20users%20supportive%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%20accused%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20of%20waging%20%E2%80%9Cflood%20jihad%E2%80%9D.%3C